---
// Landing page — custom layout, not Starlight
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Sidemesh — Your agent workstation, from anywhere</title>
<meta name="description" content="Run coding agents on your own Mac, VPS, or workstation. Control sessions, approvals, files, terminals, port forwarding, and browser previews from your phone or desktop." />
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0d0f14" />
<meta property="og:title" content="Sidemesh — Your agent workstation, from anywhere" />
<meta property="og:description" content="Sidemesh pairs a small daemon on your own machines with an iOS app for sessions, approvals, files, terminals, ports, and browser previews." />
<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
<meta property="og:image" content="/assets/og-card-v1.png" />
<meta property="og:image:alt" content="Sidemesh — agent workstation control from anywhere." />
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
<meta name="twitter:image" content="/assets/og-card-v1.png" />
<meta name="twitter:image:alt" content="Sidemesh — agent workstation control from anywhere." />
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/favicon.png" />
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/assets/app-icon.png" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
  /* ── Design tokens ── */
  :root {
    --bg:             #0d0f14;
    --bg-2:           #131519;
    --bg-3:           #191c23;
    --border:         rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    --border-strong:  rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    --text:           #ece9e3;
    --text-2:         #8b8e9c;
    --text-3:         #4d5060;
    --accent:         #f97316;
    --accent-dim:     rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.12);
    --green:          #34d399;
    --green-dim:      rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.08);
    --terminal-bg:    #07090d;
    --ease:           cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    --wrap:           min(1100px, calc(100% - 48px));
    --r:              16px;
  }

  /* ── Reset ── */
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }

  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    text-size-adjust: 100%;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    color: var(--text);
    background-color: var(--bg);
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 12% -8%, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.07), transparent),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 88% 14%, rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.04), transparent);
    font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  ::selection {
    background: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.2);
  }

  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
  p, li { text-wrap: pretty; margin: 0; }
  code { font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace; }

  .wrap {
    width: var(--wrap);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ── Skip link ── */
  .skip-link {
    position: fixed;
    top: 12px;
    left: 12px;
    z-index: 40;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--bg-2);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    transform: translateY(-200%);
    transition: transform 180ms var(--ease);
  }

  .skip-link:focus {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* ── Nav ── */
  .nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 20;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: rgba(13, 15, 20, 0.88);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  }

  .nav-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    min-height: 70px;
  }

  .brand {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .brand-logo {
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    border-radius: 9px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--border-strong);
    display: block;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: nowrap;
    gap: 2px;
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-2);
  }

  .nav-links a {
    padding: 8px 11px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: color 150ms, background 150ms;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover,
  .nav-links a:focus-visible {
    color: var(--text);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .nav-cta {
    margin-left: 10px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── Buttons ── */
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 7px;
    min-height: 42px;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition:
      transform 200ms var(--ease),
      background 200ms var(--ease),
      border-color 200ms var(--ease),
      box-shadow 200ms var(--ease);
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover,
  .btn-primary:focus-visible {
    background: #ea6d10;
    border-color: #ea6d10;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.16);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-color: var(--border-strong);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover,
  .btn-secondary:focus-visible {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    border-color: transparent;
    color: var(--text-2);
    padding-left: 4px;
    padding-right: 4px;
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover,
  .btn-ghost:focus-visible {
    color: var(--text);
    background: transparent;
  }

  .btn-ghost::after {
    content: " →";
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .btn:active {
    transform: translateY(1px) scale(0.99);
  }

  /* ── Eyebrow label ── */
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 9px;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .eyebrow::before {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-dim);
    content: "";
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── Hero ── */
  .hero {
    padding: 88px 0 72px;
  }

  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(300px, 420px);
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    margin: 20px 0 16px;
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.94;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hero .lede {
    max-width: 32rem;
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.68;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }

  .hero-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 26px;
    padding-top: 22px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .pill::before {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--green-dim);
    content: "";
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── Terminal block ── */
  .terminal {
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    background: var(--terminal-bg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03),
      0 32px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55),
      0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .terminal-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    padding: 13px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .terminal-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .terminal-dot:nth-child(1) { background: #ff5f57; }
  .terminal-dot:nth-child(2) { background: #febc2e; }
  .terminal-dot:nth-child(3) { background: #28c840; }

  .terminal-title {
    margin-left: 6px;
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-3);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: 22px;
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 2;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
  }

  .t-dim   { color: var(--text-3); }
  .t-cmt   { color: #4d5870; }
  .t-prompt { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
  .t-cmd   { color: var(--text); }
  .t-ok    { color: var(--green); }
  .t-val   { color: #93c5fd; }
  .t-gap   { display: block; height: 4px; }

  /* ── Section base ── */
  .section {
    padding: 108px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .section-lead {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .section-lead h2 {
    margin: 14px 0 14px;
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    text-wrap: balance;
    max-width: 15ch;
  }

  .section-lead p {
    max-width: 36rem;
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.68;
  }

  /* ── Feature grid ── */
  /* gap:1px + bg = visible 1px grid lines */
  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--r);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .feature-card {
    padding: 28px 24px;
    background: var(--bg-2);
    transition: background 200ms;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    background: var(--bg-3);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 38px;
    height: 38px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--accent-dim);
    border: 1px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.18);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    color: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 9px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-size: 0.91rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ── How it works: steps ── */
  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .step {
    padding-top: 22px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-num {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .step h3 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .step p {
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-size: 0.91rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ── Hero phone frame ── */
  .hero-phone {
    width: min(300px, 100%);
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-height: 560px;
    border-radius: 44px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    background: #060810;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04),
      0 40px 100px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7),
      0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .hero-phone img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ── Screenshot gallery ── */
  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .gallery-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .gallery-frame {
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 480px;
    border-radius: 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    background: #060810;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03),
      0 24px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
  }

  .gallery-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .gallery-caption {
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-3);
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ── Install section ── */
  .install-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--r);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .install-card {
    padding: 28px 24px;
    background: var(--bg-2);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .install-num {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .install-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 1.18rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .install-card > p {
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-size: 0.91rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .code-block {
    margin-top: 18px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--terminal-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    line-height: 2;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .code-block .p { color: var(--accent); }

  .install-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  /* ── Security ── */
  .security-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .security-copy h2 {
    margin: 14px 0 14px;
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.4vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .security-copy p {
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .security-copy p + p {
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .route-diagram {
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: var(--r);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg-2);
  }

  .route-label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-3);
  }

  .route-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .route-item:first-of-type {
    border-top: none;
  }

  .route-from {
    color: var(--text-2);
  }

  .route-to {
    color: var(--text-2);
    text-align: right;
  }

  .route-via {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--green);
    white-space: nowrap;
    padding: 0 4px;
  }

  .route-via::before,
  .route-via::after {
    display: block;
    height: 1px;
    min-width: 14px;
    flex: 1;
    background: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.2);
    content: "";
  }

  .route-note {
    margin-top: 18px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.83rem;
    color: var(--text-3);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── FAQ ── */
  .faq-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .faq-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(180px, 240px) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .faq-item strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    align-self: start;
    padding-top: 1px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    line-height: 1.68;
  }

  /* ── Closing CTA ── */
  .closing {
    padding: 100px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .closing-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: end;
    padding: 44px;
    border-radius: 22px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 80% at 0% 60%, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.08), transparent),
      var(--bg-2);
  }

  .closing-card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.6vw, 3.4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    text-wrap: balance;
    max-width: 14ch;
  }

  .closing-card p {
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    max-width: 34rem;
    line-height: 1.68;
  }

  .closing-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: flex-end;
  }

  /* ── Footer ── */
  footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 24px 0 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-3);
  }

  footer nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  footer a {
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: var(--text-3);
    transition: color 150ms, background 150ms;
  }

  footer a:hover {
    color: var(--text);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  }

  /* ── Focus ── */
  :focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
    outline-offset: 3px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .hero-phone {
      width: min(260px, 100%);
      max-height: 480px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .terminal {
      max-width: 480px;
    }

    .feature-grid,
    .steps-grid,
    .install-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .security-inner,
    .closing-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .closing-actions {
      align-items: flex-start;
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 84px 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .hero-phone {
      display: none;
    }

    .gallery-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .gallery-frame {
      border-radius: 20px;
      max-height: 320px;
    }

    :root {
      --wrap: min(calc(100% - 32px), 1100px);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: none;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 52px 0 56px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 13vw, 3.8rem);
    }

    .hero-actions,
    .install-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .btn-primary,
    .btn-secondary {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      width: auto;
    }

    .feature-grid,
    .steps-grid,
    .install-grid,
    .faq-item {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .closing-card {
      padding: 28px;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .closing-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    footer {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 72px 0;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .feature-card,
    .install-card,
    .step {
      animation: rise 560ms var(--ease) both;
    }

    .feature-card:nth-child(2),
    .install-card:nth-child(2),
    .step:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 60ms; }

    .feature-card:nth-child(3),
    .install-card:nth-child(3),
    .step:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 120ms; }

    .feature-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 80ms; }
    .feature-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 140ms; }
    .feature-card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 200ms; }
  }

  @keyframes rise {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to content</a>

  <!-- ── Nav ── -->
  <header class="nav">
    <div class="wrap nav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Sidemesh home">
        <img class="brand-logo" src="/assets/app-icon.png" alt="" width="30" height="30" aria-hidden="true" />
        <span>Sidemesh</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Primary">
        <a href="#features">Features</a>
        <a href="#install">Install</a>
        <a href="#security">Security</a>
        <a href="/getting-started/">Docs</a>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/URvvnN7Dv" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Discord</a>
      </nav>
      <div class="nav-cta">
        <a
          class="btn btn-primary"
          href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/UZ6FTc9r"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          Join iOS Beta
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main">

    <!-- ── Hero ── -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="wrap hero-grid">

        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">iOS Beta · Open Now</span>
          <h1>Control your coding agents <em>from anywhere.</em></h1>
          <p class="lede">
            Sidemesh runs beside your coding agents on the machines you trust,
            then gives you the remote surface around them: sessions, approvals,
            files, terminals, ports, and previews from your phone or desktop.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a
              class="btn btn-primary"
              href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/UZ6FTc9r"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
            >
              Join iOS Beta
            </a>
            <a
              class="btn btn-secondary"
              href="https://discord.gg/URvvnN7Dv"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
            >
              Join Discord
            </a>
            <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/getting-started/">Read the docs</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-pills" role="list" aria-label="Key properties">
            <span class="pill" role="listitem">your machines</span>
            <span class="pill" role="listitem">private network first</span>
            <span class="pill" role="listitem">no cloud workspace</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-phone">
          <img
            src="/assets/screenshots/session-actions.png"
            alt="Sidemesh session actions: terminal, port forwarding, resources, transcript search, and more."
            width="640"
            height="1391"
            loading="eager"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Features ── -->
    <section class="section" id="features">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-lead">
          <span class="eyebrow">What you get</span>
          <h2>The missing layer around coding agents.</h2>
          <p>
            Chat is only one part of supervising an agent. Sidemesh keeps the rest of
            the workstation close too: approvals, files, git context, terminals,
            ports, and previews.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-grid">

          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="1" y="2" width="16" height="12" rx="2"/>
                <path d="M6 16h6M9 14v2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Session control</h3>
            <p>Running sessions, pending approvals, transcript events, and host status — reachable across all paired machines from one place.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M9 2l2 5h5l-4 3 1.5 5L9 12l-4.5 3L6 10 2 7h5z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Approvals, surfaced</h3>
            <p>Blocked sessions don't stay blocked. Pending decisions get their own space instead of disappearing into transcript history.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M10 2H4a1 1 0 00-1 1v12a1 1 0 001 1h10a1 1 0 001-1V7l-5-5z"/>
                <path d="M10 2v5h5M6 10h6M6 13h4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Workspace inspection</h3>
            <p>Browse files, render markdown, review git context, and inspect generated assets before approving the agent's next step.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="1" y="2" width="16" height="14" rx="2"/>
                <path d="M5 7l3 3-3 3M10 13h4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Terminal access</h3>
            <p>Attach to a host shell when chat is not enough. Deliberately gated — kept behind the private network where host access is intentional.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="4.5" cy="9" r="2.5"/>
                <circle cx="13.5" cy="9" r="2.5"/>
                <path d="M7 9h4"/>
                <path d="M10.5 7.5l2.5 1.5-2.5 1.5"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Port forwarding</h3>
            <p>Reach dev servers running on the remote machine from your phone or desktop — without exposing the host to the public internet.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="1" y="3" width="16" height="13" rx="2"/>
                <path d="M1 7h16M5 5h.01M7.5 5h.01M10 5h.01"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Browser preview</h3>
            <p>Stream a live browser running on the host when visual state matters. No tunnel, no staging server, no extra tooling needed.</p>
          </article>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── App screenshots ── -->
    <section class="section" id="screenshots">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-lead">
          <span class="eyebrow">In the app</span>
          <h2>See what you're installing.</h2>
          <p>Real screenshots from the current iOS build. Terminal access, file browsing, and live session view. Dark by default.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-grid">
          <div class="gallery-item">
            <div class="gallery-frame">
              <img
                src="/assets/screenshots/terminal.png"
                alt="Sidemesh live terminal showing a vite dev server running on the host."
                width="640"
                height="1391"
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
              />
            </div>
            <span class="gallery-caption">Terminal access</span>
          </div>
          <div class="gallery-item">
            <div class="gallery-frame">
              <img
                src="/assets/screenshots/file-browser.png"
                alt="Sidemesh file browser showing astro.config.mjs with syntax highlighting."
                width="640"
                height="1391"
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
              />
            </div>
            <span class="gallery-caption">File browser</span>
          </div>
          <div class="gallery-item">
            <div class="gallery-frame">
              <img
                src="/assets/screenshots/session.png"
                alt="Sidemesh session view showing a live agent transcript."
                width="640"
                height="1391"
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
              />
            </div>
            <span class="gallery-caption">Session view</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── How it works ── -->
    <section class="section" id="how">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-lead">
          <span class="eyebrow">How it works</span>
          <h2>Install the host. Pair the app. Stay close.</h2>
          <p>
            Your code stays where it already lives. The daemon runs next to your agents,
            credentials, and development servers on the machines you control.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="steps-grid">
          <article class="step">
            <span class="step-num">01 — Install</span>
            <h3>Run the daemon where your agents run.</h3>
            <p>
              One <code>npm install</code> and <code style="color:var(--accent)">sidemesh up</code> is enough.
              Run it on a Mac, VPS, or workstation. Pair over Tailscale, a VPN, or a local network.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <span class="step-num">02 — Pair</span>
            <h3>Pair the app over your private route.</h3>
            <p>
              The daemon prints a pairing URL on first run. Scan it in the iOS app.
              Sessions, approvals, and all host surfaces become immediately reachable.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <span class="step-num">03 — Work</span>
            <h3>Drop into the right tool for the job.</h3>
            <p>
              Reply in chat, clear an approval, browse files, attach a terminal,
              forward a port, or stream the browser — from anywhere, in one app.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Install ── -->
    <section class="section" id="install">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-lead">
          <span class="eyebrow">Install</span>
          <h2>Install the host. Join the beta. Pair once.</h2>
          <p>
            The iOS beta is open now. Install the daemon on a trusted machine,
            pair over your private network, and use Discord if setup gets weird.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="install-grid">

          <article class="install-card">
            <span class="install-num">01 — Host daemon</span>
            <h3>Start on each trusted machine.</h3>
            <p>
              Install the package, run setup, install the service to survive restarts,
              then pair with the generated URL. Machines pair independently.
            </p>
            <div class="code-block" aria-label="Install commands">
              <span class="p">$</span> npm install -g sidemesh @openai/codex<br />
              <span class="p">$</span> sidemesh up<br />
              <span class="p">$</span> sidemesh service install
            </div>
            <div class="install-actions">
              <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/getting-started/">Read the docs</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="install-card">
            <span class="install-num">02 — iOS beta</span>
            <h3>Join TestFlight once the host is reachable.</h3>
            <p>
              The app is the daily surface: sessions, approvals, files, terminal,
              previews, usage, and host management. Install the daemon first.
            </p>
            <div class="install-actions" style="margin-top: auto; padding-top: 24px;">
              <a
                class="btn btn-primary"
                href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/UZ6FTc9r"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
              >
                Open TestFlight
              </a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="install-card">
            <span class="install-num">03 — Community</span>
            <h3>Discord is the fast path for help.</h3>
            <p>
              Setup friction, provider quirks, and bug reports land better in a
              live conversation than a quiet inbox. Come find us there.
            </p>
            <div class="install-actions" style="margin-top: auto; padding-top: 24px;">
              <a
                class="btn btn-secondary"
                href="https://discord.gg/URvvnN7Dv"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
              >
                Join Discord
              </a>
            </div>
          </article>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Security ── -->
    <section class="section" id="security">
      <div class="wrap security-inner">

        <div class="security-copy">
          <span class="eyebrow">Security model</span>
          <h2>Powerful host access belongs on a private route.</h2>
          <p>
            Sidemesh can reach transcripts, approvals, files, terminals, forwarded
            ports, and browser sessions. That is what makes it useful — and why
            you should run it over Tailscale, WireGuard, or a trusted LAN.
          </p>
          <p>
            Do not casually expose a daemon with host-level capabilities to the open
            internet. Keep the network boundary explicit.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="route-diagram" role="img" aria-label="Private network route: phone and desktop connect through a private route to the daemon host, which connects locally to the agent and workspace">
          <span class="route-label">private network route</span>
          <div class="route-item">
            <span class="route-from">iPhone / desktop</span>
            <span class="route-via">private</span>
            <span class="route-to">daemon host</span>
          </div>
          <div class="route-item">
            <span class="route-from">daemon</span>
            <span class="route-via">local</span>
            <span class="route-to">agent + tools</span>
          </div>
          <div class="route-item">
            <span class="route-from">agent</span>
            <span class="route-via">local</span>
            <span class="route-to">workspace + fs</span>
          </div>
          <p class="route-note">
            Tailscale and WireGuard both work out of the box. The daemon listens
            on whatever address you give it — keep that address off the public internet.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── FAQ ── -->
    <section class="section" id="faq">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-lead">
          <span class="eyebrow">FAQ</span>
          <h2>Plain answers before you install.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <strong>Is this a cloud IDE?</strong>
            <p>No. Sidemesh does not host your code or move your workspace. It connects to a daemon running on your own Mac, VPS, or workstation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <strong>Do I need the daemon before TestFlight?</strong>
            <p>Yes. The mobile app becomes useful once a trusted host is installed, running, and reachable over the same private network as your device. Start with the daemon.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <strong>Which agents does it support today?</strong>
            <p>The iOS beta focuses on Codex sessions. The daemon is provider-based, so the same host surface works as more providers are added. Copilot CLI is also supported.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <strong>Should I expose the daemon to the internet?</strong>
            <p>No. Use a private route first. The daemon is intentionally close to powerful host capabilities — terminal, files, approvals, ports. Treat that boundary seriously.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <strong>How is this different from SSH?</strong>
            <p>SSH gives you a shell. Sidemesh gives you the agent-aware view: running sessions, pending approvals, transcripts, files, git context, ports, previews, and terminal access when you need it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Closing ── -->
    <section class="closing">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="closing-card">
          <div>
            <h2>Carry the workstation surface, not the workstation.</h2>
            <p>
              Install Sidemesh on the hosts you trust, join the iOS beta, and stay
              close to your agents when your laptop is not in front of you.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="closing-actions">
            <a
              class="btn btn-primary"
              href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/UZ6FTc9r"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
            >
              Join iOS Beta
            </a>
            <a
              class="btn btn-secondary"
              href="https://discord.gg/URvvnN7Dv"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
            >
              Join Discord
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <footer class="wrap">
    <span>Sidemesh — private agent workstation</span>
    <nav aria-label="Footer links">
      <a href="/getting-started/">Docs</a>
      <a href="/support">Support</a>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
      <a href="https://discord.gg/URvvnN7Dv" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Discord</a>
    </nav>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
